Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,== Dialogue ============================

Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice one, Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it, Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All you, Mami!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Five seconds left!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The bonds of our hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The bonds of our hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The bonds of our hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...connect the puck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! Our dream finally came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Time for our Victory Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We are Smile Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ (One, two!) ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ Wow wow wow yay!\NWow wow wow victory! ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ Wow wow wow yay!\NEverybody say go! ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ The sun's sparkling!\NThings are heating up! ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ Even on the ice?\N(We're getting fired up!) ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ One swing of the stick\Ncan turn everything around! ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ Let's dance!\N(Let's dance!) ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ Sweet and bittersweet memories.\NKinda like matcha {\i1}manju{\i0}? ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ The tasty parts are...\N(We are...) The best! Sunrise! ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ Connect our feelings! Go! ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ Chase with all we've got\Ntill we've grasped it! ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ We meet at last!\NFaster and stronger, ride the tailwind! ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:03:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ It's not in the rule books--\NWe've got our own motto: "Shooting!" ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ Next time we light up the goal...\NExpect sun, followed by dreaming! ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher pulled Mana aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,--Really?\N--Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:04:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you do this time, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing! It was committee stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's {\i1}senbei {\i0}are good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk with your mouth full.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Want tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,--Here.\N--Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,--Gather up!\N--Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm! Nothing says springtime\Nof youth like sweat and sports!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Our embroidery club counts, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! It's existed\Nsince Grandma's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stitch by stitch, we've made\Nmasterpieces across generations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We all share a common thread!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. As president of such a\Ntime-honored club, quit talking and work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aya, let her drink tea in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too easy on her, Kao! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too easy on her, Kao! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:04:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then... Oh! It's a tough one today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's what makes it\Nfulfilling when you finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a sense of accomplishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! You've got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Move your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up. I'm image training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For embroidery?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Mami! You get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! Stop humoring her, Mami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At last!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That was hard today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It's so pretty! That's Mami for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In comparison, yours looks crude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called being bold!\NYours doesn't even match the pattern!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called being unique!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What a neat color choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're giddy when Mami praises you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for today! Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah!\N--Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kinunoyado\NShikiootoro\NPardon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, there's a stitch I kinda need\Nhelp with. Can you show me later?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's do our thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Soakin' it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,An open-air bath whenever we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the perks of being friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey! They wanna film at our {\i1}ryokan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,For a drama? A movie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A variety show, or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:07:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean by, "or something"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom got so excited by the call,\Nshe can't even remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're mailing the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you think it's a TV\Nspecial about you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,--Eh?!\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cute Next-Gen Hostesses\Nof an Age-Old {\i1}Ryokan{\i0}."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, "Newbie Hostesses at Work."\NThose sorta shows are trending!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,--They sure are!\N--Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure we're here for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,For "Cute Hostesses and Their\NSupport Crew," or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You just wanted to say "cute hostesses."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret's out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, the producer must have\Na good eye to pick our {\i1}ryokan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Spouting more self-praise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I "sing" my own praises.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Strawberries from Yanagida\NFarms are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:07:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So juicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And super sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I could eat a million!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. My dad would be\Nhappy to hear you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis! Stop chowing 'em down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay! They're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one dousing 'em\Nin condensed milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It overpowers the strawberry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Grr! The milk elevates\Nthe strawberry taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Salty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In perfect sync.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? How about strawberries?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat 'em plain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,With condensed milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where they differ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Very curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:09:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was late today 'cuz I got asked to\Nput something on the bulletin board!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice hockey hands-on trial class?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikko's pro team, the Dream Monkeys,\Nis putting it on this Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You two can skate, right?\NWe did it in gym class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it sound cool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be worth trying out, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice hockey, huh? That sounds\Npretty scary. Won't we get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine! It'll be an experience!\NC'mon, let's all go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma always says,\N"Try new experiences!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. I doubt she meant ice hockey\Nby that. Still, it might be fun to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:10:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's worth a shot!\NI'm up for trying it once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?! Let's do it, Mami!\NLet's all go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm! I'll give it a go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! That settles it! I'll apply for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. Once you wrap the thread, use\Nyour left hand to pull and right to push.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that's how you do it!\NAll right! Thanks, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. You're so\Npassionate about learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a project I'm trying to\Nfinish before second semester ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. But don't focus too hard\Nor your eyes will go bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww! Anything but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate the Poor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Let's play again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been here\Nsince our gym field trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When does ice hockey season start?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a little late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cuz Ayaka overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh! You wouldn't get up\Nso I fell asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough excuses! C'mon, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up! Let's start\Nthis season with spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Be kind! Make 'em think:\N"I wanna come back next week!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It starts with: "Ice hockey is kinda fun!"\NAnd then: "Maybe I'll go next week!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon enough: "Maybe I'll join the\NDream Monkeys!" Can't you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon enough: "Maybe I'll join the\NDream Monkeys!" Can't you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?! You need to be super nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,--This is what you've been training for!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--Um, Yoko?\N--This is what you've been training for!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Sato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making a face\Nthat'll scare 'em away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew! I've got wrinkles here?! Since when?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your issue? Huh?\NYoko, they're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Sato, put it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here for the trial class?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Kirifuri Arena!\NMy, you're all so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Kinugawa Junior High\N3rd year, Manaka Mizusawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoruko Yanagida, Mami Ono,\Nand 2nd year, Ayaka Mizusawa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:13:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming to the ice hockey\Ntrial class! Let's head on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,--Brr!\N--It's chilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Change into your gym clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, are you guys participating\Nin the trial class, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So are we!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Manaka Mizusawa,\Na 3rd year at Kinugawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Riko Saginuma from Kirifuri.\NAnd here's my extra, Naomi Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're 3rd years, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me an extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! It's all girls this year!\NAnd what a harvest at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In junior high, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine! It's an early harvest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, my ambition will come to light!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, that one idea of mixing\Nice hockey and entertainment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! First, I'll train the girls to play\Nlike proper Dream Monkeys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But after each win, they'll do\Na victory dance on the ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a clever performance\Nwill delight the audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll bring in people who never\Nhad interest in ice hockey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll appear in my old uniform\Nand sing a song while I'm at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll attract the biggest\Ncrowds you've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,More like your delusion.\NYou're saying some pretty crazy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, don't you dare\Nlet these girls slip away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, we'll start with warm-ups\Nto help prevent injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stretch along to a rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice hockey uses a lot of muscles.\NWe'll do upper body first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,--One, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--Interesting stretch!\N--One, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,--It sure is!\N--One, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Two, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's one more useful for games. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,--This clearly isn't a stretch.\N--Two, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's more like a step.\N--Two, two, three, four,\Nfive, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't a step! It's a dance\Nused to evade defenders!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,--She said "dance" clear as day.\N--Three, four, five, six, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah.\N--Two, three, four, five,\Nsix, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,--This is fun!\N--Two, three, four, five,\Nsix, seven, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's keeping up, right?\NOn to the next dance routine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance routine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing great! Now that you've\Nwarmed up, let's get you on the rink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You can change into\Nyour uniforms this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At last!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah.\N--We get to wear uniforms!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,These girls... This could work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that phony\Nstretch dance thing was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If it went any longer, I would've left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now. The fun's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It looks like a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. It's lighter than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We can move easy in these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like so much. If someone\Nruns into you, won't it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. In girls' hockey, body checking\Nis an illegal hit. It shouldn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel stoked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:17:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, guys! The trial class\Nstarts now! Let's rock and roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"Rock and roll"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it safe to say everyone can skate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! That's the locals for you.\NTry to keep up with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird skating in gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Ayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is edge control!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Control it! Go slow if needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, you've warmed up to the rink,\Nso let's talk about the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Games last for 60 minutes,\Nbroken into three, 20-minute periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Two teams compete to score\Nthe most goals in that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There're two pieces of\Nequipment you need to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The first is a puck. You score\Nby hitting it in the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about as big as a {\i1}jingoro senbei{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made of black rubber\Nand is very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be sorry if it\Nhits you, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. I don't wanna get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoko, what are you scaring 'em for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is a hockey stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a bath-stirring stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You use the stick to control\Nthe puck by moving it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you guys try it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:19:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Nobody's good at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone get in a circle\Nand practice passing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizusawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it! Here it comes, Mami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice stop, Mami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys did great today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of hockey?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was rusty since I haven't skated\Nin a while, but it came back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm new to using a stick,\Nbut it was kinda fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sad we couldn't play more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I count on you to show up next week?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping for "okey-dokey."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so old-fashioned, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you all had fun!\NBe careful heading home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! That was so much fun!\NThe hours just flew by!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! It was over before I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fun experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you'll come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice hockey was fun! Passing the puck\Naround... Everyone chasing after it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I love embroidery. Stitch by stitch,\Nwatching a project come together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's such a sense of accomplishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But today, connecting the puck\Naround was really neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For us to work together like that...\NIt was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So... So...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play ice hockey next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mami...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you're the one saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it again next week, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okey-dokey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Old-fashioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In that moment, I--no, we... discovered\Nour sparkling springtime of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.00,0:23:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Connect the puck, even in a game!
